							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Electrical Issues</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						If your heating system is causing circuit breakers to trip repeatedly, or if you notice sparking or other
						electrical problems, turn off the system and call for emergency service to prevent electrical fires.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

